    "NUNAVUT": "NU",
    "YUKON TERRITORY": "YT"
};

var abbr = {};

exports.full = full;


for (var i in full) {
    abbr[full[i]] = i;
}

exports.abbr = abbr;

exports.normalize = function(state) {
    state = state.toUpperCase();

    if (state.length !== 2) {
        state = full[state];
    }
    return state;
}
